{"TopicId":204652,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Multiple Monitors","CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-02T20:15:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-02T20:15:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is certainly not a priority, but it would be very cool if KSP2 supported dual monitors.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI apologize if this has been suggested already.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qwery123","CreatedById":214461,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-18T18:43:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be cool if we could do different things (such as normal gameplay on one and IVA on another) on each screen if we have dual screens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-18T20:17:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224033679\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204652\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631990584\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214461\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qwery123\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, qwery123 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be cool if we could do different things (such as normal gameplay on one and IVA on another) on each screen if we have dual screens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is possible with Telemagic, I believe\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DfA-DoM","CreatedById":160709,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-20T09:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquot