uthorid=\u0022185092\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6562375229\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/179887-*\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:196px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou are correct, I was on mobile when I answered.\u00A0 Close, though \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-20T11:37:21Z\u0022 title=\u002209/20/2021 11:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 20, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by linuxgurugamer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-20T12:22:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, what about this mod:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.curseforge.com/kerbal/ksp-mods/kerbal-telemetry\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.curseforge.com/kerbal/ksp-mods/kerbal-telemetry\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/yagiziskirik/Kerbal-Telemetry\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/yagiziskirik/Kerbal-Telemetry\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIsn\u0027t there an official forum thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-20T12:23:39Z\u0022 title=\u002209/20/2021 12:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 20, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by antipro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-21T15:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm...\u00A0 Multiple monitor support. That\u00A0one caused a heated debate a little while ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot highest priority, but\u00A0yes I would welcome it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-21T20:38:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224034642\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204652\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221632239508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm...\u00A0 Multiple monitor support. That\u00A0one caused a heated debate a little while ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot highest priority, but\u00A0yes I would welcome it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA heated debate?\u00A0 Interesting.\u00A0 What is there to get heated about?\u00A0 It does not seem like the type of thing to elicit strong reactions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-21T21:46:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224034733\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204652\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221632256689\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181256\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Klapaucius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Klapaucius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA heated debate?\u00A0 Interesting.\u00A0 What is there to get heated about?\u00A0 It does not seem like the type of thing to elicit strong reactions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhether or not this is the kind of thing to elicit strong reactions, I can\u0027t know that.\u003Cbr\u003E\nFor my part, I have always had multimonitor configurations, and apart from that,\u003Cbr\u003E\nwho today does not have a pc with 2 monitors or just a notebook connected to a TV?\u003Cbr\u003E\nThat said, ever since I started playing KSP, ie before the release of \u00221.2: Loud and Clear\u0022,\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027ve always wanted to have the rocket view on the main monitor and the map on the secondary.\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo, imho, it should be a must have feature.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-22T02:19:56Z\u0022 title=\u002209/22/2021 02:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 22, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by antipro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TBenz","CreatedById":190349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T00:48:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224034733\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204652\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221632256689\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181256\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Klapaucius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Klapaucius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA heated debate?\u00A0 Interesting.\u00A0 What is there to get heated about?\u00A0 It does not seem like the type of thing to elicit strong reactions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome people without dual monitor setups\u00A0took extreme issue with\u00A0the suggestion that Intercept \u0022waste\u0022 any amount of development time on a feature they wouldn\u0027t use.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T03:52:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d assume if there is multi-player (and we know there is) then multi-monitor should be there unless it\u0027s some split screen deal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}